# PalSchema Mod Store - Git Ignore Configuration

# ===========================================
# Mod Files (Large zip files, icons, etc.)
# ===========================================
# Exclude the entire mods directory to avoid syncing large mod files locally
# The mods folder will still exist on GitHub (added by automated workflows)
# but won't be downloaded to local development machines
mods/

# However, keep the ExampleMod for reference and testing
!mods/ExampleMod/
!mods/ExampleMod/**

# Ignore SubmissionTest mod locally (but keep on GitHub)
mods/SubmissionTest/
mods/SubmissionTest/**

