# ===========================================
# Note for Developers
# ===========================================
# The mods/ directory is excluded by default to prevent downloading
# hundreds of mod files to local development machines.
# 
# If you need to work with specific mods locally:
# 1. Create a local test folder: mkdir temp_mods
# 2. Download specific mods you need to test
# 3. The automated workflows will still manage the real mods/ folder on GitHub
#
# To temporarily include mods folder: git add mods/ --force